title: Weekly Review with Clay and Buck H1 - Feb 19 2022
itunes:title: Weekly Review with Clay and Buck H1 - Feb 19 2022
description:
A hundred million people witness the left's mask hypocrisy at Super Bowl in Los Angeles, while California children are still required to wear masks in school. De Santis: The medical science didn't change, the political science changed. Fauci has disappeared, not currently in the media repertoire? Rep. Jayapal: Not wearing a mask in the Capitol Hill elevators is the same as Jan. 6th. Will you be surprised by the new F-word in Canada? The Super Bowl halftime show, Buck says was a throwback for those who went to high school in the '90s. Clay says Hollywood no longer knows how to talk to the masses and Oscar-nominated movies prove that.
